RelatedSentence: The first meeting for volunteers for The I Believe Teen Moms Empowerment Conference will be held Thursday at 6 p.m. at the Orchard Knob Middle School Community Room , located at 500 North Highland Park Avenue .

The I Believe Teen Moms Empowerment Conference is a community supported event will provide education , empowerment , and access to mentors and resources for Chattanooga area teen moms as they navigate toward their individual levels of success .
